</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="AD3836FFFFF9647FFF20C400A346FA06" blockId="18.[188,1401,1318,1486]" pageId="18" pageNumber="29">
The name 
<taxonomicName id="6A874D7CFFF9647FFEDCC401A3E0FA8A" authority="Golikov, 1980" authorityName="Golikov" authorityYear="1980" box="[321,742,1318,1345]" class="Gastropoda" family="Buccinidae" genus="Buccinum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="18" pageNumber="29" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="costatum">
<emphasis id="9FF3EAEDFFF9647FFEDCC401A328FA8B" box="[321,558,1319,1344]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="29">Buccinum costatum</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="C9164B0EFFF9647FFDA7C400A3E0FA8A" author="Golikov A. N." box="[570,742,1318,1345]" pageId="18" pageNumber="29" pagination="2" refId="ref11612" refString="Golikov A. N. 1980. Molluscs Buccininae of the World Ocean. Fauna of USSR, Mollusks 5 (2). Nauka Publ., Leningrad." type="journal article" year="1980">Golikov, 1980</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
is a junior primary homonym of 
<taxonomicName id="6A874D7CFFF9647FFB14C401A072FAAE" authority="Linnaeus, 1758" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1758" class="Gastropoda" family="Buccinidae" genus="Buccinum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="18" pageNumber="29" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="costatum">
<emphasis id="9FF3EAEDFFF9647FFB14C401A470FA8B" box="[1161,1398,1319,1344]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="29">Buccinum costatum</emphasis>
Linnaeus, 1758
</taxonomicName>
